	   <tr><td colspan=2>By successfully hiding, then successfully sneaking, any rogue can move about totally invisible, though very slowly.&nbsp;&nbsp; Be aware that when you zone, your hiding will be removed, and you will be exposed to the naked eye.  Also, if anybody has the spell See Invisible or another similar spell's effects on them, they will detect you (which I never understood; you're supposed to be hiding behind something, how does a magic spell chance that?)<br><br>Or, well, I suppose you could kill the guards.  If you opt for this option, I have a class for you: a little proffession I call the Warrior.<br><br>Nothing in the way of a guise for evil rogues, though, which is odd, considering that we should be able to infiltrate into their towns as well as they can into ours.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
